SECTION 5 ◆ SUMMARY — THE MENTAL MODEL
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  A Proxy is like a protective shield or a smart assistant.

  - FORWARD Proxy: Protects/Speeds up the USER.
    "I will go get that website for you so they don't know who you are."

  - REVERSE Proxy: Protects/Speeds up the SERVER.
    "I will handle the millions of users so the web server doesn't explode."

